dct_title_s: Map of Allegany County showing the topography and election districts
dct_description_sm: Shows the topography and election districts of Allegany County, Maryland. Waterways and man-made features such as roads, railroads, bridges, and buildings are indicated.
Map.; Title from cataloger.; Includes legend. Relief shown by contours and spot heights.
